infos.value: Vinera... What's the meaning of this?
Heh heh. You still don't get it!?
So it's true. You really are the craven prince who cowers away from battle.
As you can see, this wench...your Vinera is no princess of Fennes.
She is an assassin sent by Fennes to take your life.
Vinera... Is this true?
...Yes.
Heh heh. How does it feel, Prince?
To die at the hands of a lowly slum rat?
Come now. If you truly pity her, then don't bother putting up a fight.
Your head is going to keep her well fed for quite some time. That's the deal, after all.
Vinera... Kill him!
Vinera...
This isn't your fault. I was just born into the wrong place, into the wrong life.
Whenever you're ready... Do it, Vinera.
Why do you hesitate!?
Has his cowardice spread to you as well!?
What's this!?
...Vinera?
Lord Dario... Stay by my side!
Becauseâ€”! Because I'll protect you!
